
Compile
------

To Compile you need:

* A C++ compiler
* CMake
* OpenCV 2.0 libraries installed
* Boost C++ libraries

first run cmake. then make. Now you have binaries


Usage
-----

In settings.h you can predefine define all settings. 
For example if you want to use a movie or video device.

First run train to train the hog classifier. Then run finder.
